text.__SUMMARY__: Impatiens obesa is a species of plant in the family Balsaminaceae. It is endemic to China.
text.Sources: China Plant Specialist Group (2004). "Impatiens obesa". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 2004: e.T46546A11066522. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.2004.RLTS.T46546A11066522.en. Retrieved 21 December 2017.
